author: Justin Hawkins Rides Again
description:
Earlier this month, there was excitement when Wolf Alice returned after a 4 year hiatus with a new single "Bloom Baby Bloom".  I've been told to listen to Wolf Alice in the past, but I didn't. I will now. 

To watch the whole video uninterrupted, visit: https://youtu.be/lBGcloF8LIY?si=VaHsldqa_E7UrtcZ

To see more from JHRA,  join my Patreon here: http://www.patreon.com/jushawk

For Cameo messages: https://www.cameo.com/justinhawkins

The latest Darkness album "Dreams On Toast" is available here: https://thedarkness.lnk.to/dreamsontoast/

title: Why Didn't I Listen?
